examples.text: Fenerbahçeli kaleci Dominik Livakovic, sezon sonuna kadar Hırvatistan ekibi Dinamo Zagreb'e kiralandı. (The Fenerbahçe goalkeeper Dominik Livakovic has been loaned to the Croatian team Dinamo Zagreb until the end of the season.)

etymology: From Fenerbahçe (“Fenerbahçe”) + -li (“-er, -ite”, suffix denoting origin or association).
